You need to create a restrictive access control list (ACL) on a server. Which policy should bethe default for the INPUT chain within the firewall?
A)  deny
B)  permit
C)  accept
D)  discard
A
A. The default policy should be deny. A deny- by- default policy discards packets. Itsnotable that a reject policy might also be used, which would send a reject back to thesender. The other options are not appropriate for the task described.
